author: Lauren Murphy
title: MusicNews | Dates and ticket details for X Factor Live 2016 in Dublin & Belfast have been announced
text:
The TV ratings for X Factor may allegedly be faltering, but apparently there's still an audience for the live shows.
A number of this year's contestants that make it to the live shows - although that has yet to be decided - will take part in the UK and Irish live tour next year.
Whoever, they are, the dates have been decided for those shows. The tour will hit Dublin's 3Arena on Friday, February 19th and Belfast's SSE Arena on Wednesday, February 17th.
Tickets are on sale from usual outlets this Friday at 9am.
